							2023 – 2024
						</span>
						<div class="text-[1rem] leading-tight">
							Research Assistant to
							<a href="https://Ronanlyons.com" class="text-link hover:underline">Ronan Lyons</a>.
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<span class="w-24 flex-none font-mono text-[0.85rem] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
							2021 – 2022
